38871>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38871>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38871>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
38871>>>>>        Handle hoDD
38871>>>>>
38871>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
38872>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
38873>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
38874>>>>>
38874>>>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
38874>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
38875>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
38876>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
38877>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to False
38878>>>>>
38878>>>>>        If (NavigateData.bReadOnly) Begin
38880>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to True
38881>>>>>        End
38881>>>>>>
38881>>>>>        Else Begin
38882>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38883>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38884>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38885>>>>>        End
38885>>>>>>
38885>>>>>    End_Procedure
